      "layout": "The layout is primarily a max-width contained design at 1305px, centered on the page. The hero features a large, centered Sana Serif headline over a white background. Sections alternate between full-width white backgrounds and contained white space. Content is arranged using a mix of centered stacks (for headings and forms) and a prominent two-column grid for product features, where text is often paired with a product showcase card. Vertical spacing between sections is generous at 62px, giving elements ample breathing room. The navigation is a minimalist top bar, right-aligned with interactive links and a prominent 'Sign in' button.",
